<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Our policy regarding Advanced Placement can be found in more detail on our Web site.  Applicants for admission who participate in the Advanced Placement Program of the College Entrance Examination Board and achieve a grade of three (3) may receive advanced placement in appropriate subject areas without college credit. Students scoring four (4) or five (5) will be granted college credit.</i>
